description.value:
The breakpoint value. The default is `0px`.

**Note**: This breakpoint value is not supported in CSS media queries.

**Example**:
```css
/* Modify the breakpoint value */
:root {
  --mdui-breakpoint-xs: 0px;
}
```

The breakpoint value. The default is `600px`.

