If you want to set this color value, it is recommended to set `--mdui-color-outline-variant-light` and `--mdui-color-outline-variant-dark` separately.

**Example**:
```css
/* Read the color value that automatically adapts */
.element {
  color: rgb(var(--mdui-color-outline-variant));
}

/* Read the color value that automatically adapts and add opacity */
.element {
  color: rgba(var(--mdui-color-outline-variant), 0.5);
}

/* Set the color values for light mode and dark mode separately */
:root {
  --mdui-color-outline-variant-light: 255, 0, 0;
  --mdui-color-outline-variant-dark: 255, 0, 0;
}
```

